fields.name: Heel-Turn (solo)
fields.description: A competition where you're free to show off your moves while keeping up with the beats and enjoying the music.

fields.name: Verve
fields.description: An event where you can flaunt your fashion sense based on a given theme, and stand apart from your fellow competitors. Come showcase your fashion sense at our themed fashion show.

fields.name: Step-Up
fields.description: From jamming in the streets to dancing to the beats, spinning on the backs, gliding on the floor, and still yelling for more. If this is your style, Anwesha presents you with the Street Battle Dance Competition  where you go to the streets and groove to the beats. Gear up to show us those kick-ass moves and compete with the best.

fields.name: The Imagination Station
fields.description: An amazing journey of speaking and debating that will take you through three extraordinary stations of JAM, PROCON, and ALTERNATE ENDING. An event to showcase your creative thinking and take yourself and people around to your own imagination station.

fields.name: The General Quiz
fields.description: A General Quiz by none other than Major Chandrakant Nair

fields.name: Heel-Turn Group
fields.description: A competition where you're free to show off your moves while keeping up with the beats and enjoying the music. Depending on your desire and ability level, you can perform in a group.

fields.name: Syngphony
fields.description: Feel the magic of music in the air. A solo singing competition for lovers of melody. The competition that shall put you among thoroughbreds of the music world. This is your chance to flaunt your vocal talent as Anwesha presents Syngphony: Anweshas premier singing contest.

fields.name: Brand-verse
fields.description: Brand-Verse is a photography competition where you take a shot of a product and style it to look appealing enough to purchase, basically marketing the product.

fields.name: Ekal
fields.description: A solo acting competition to put yourself in your favorite character's shoes. An event to turn the spotlight towards yourself and showcase your acting skills, coordination, expressions, and stellar dialogue delivery.

fields.name: Darpan
fields.description: A wall painting competition where people have to express their creativity and imagination on the walls in the form of graffiti and paintings concerning the theme.

fields.name: Satanz Tantrum
fields.description: Santanz Tantrum is a musical band competition where people will form a musical band team and compete for the title of best band.

fields.name: Maidan-E-Jung
fields.description: An event where many characters that stick to heart, stories that are larger than life, and exchange of ideologies come to life with theatrical performances by participants. Street plays are also one of the most original and oldest ways of acting, which brings out talent in performers and a connecting experience for the audience.

fields.name: Chal Chitra
fields.description: Do films inspire you? Its time for you to amass artists passionate about the visual arts and bring all your ideas to life. Anwesha 2023 is ecstatic to present an online short film-making competition. Let the creative juices flow!

fields.name: BeSpoke
fields.description: An exciting event with an opportunity to quench your poetic thirst and satisfy all your literary cravings. A platform to recite your original written piece in poetry, musing and shayari. An event to pen down all your feelings you never expressed and the thoughts you never shared.

fields.name: Chalawaran
fields.description: From hunting camouflage to religious decoration to military subterfuge..let the colors splash! Whether youre a beginner or a seasoned artist, come and compete with others who share your passion for painting. Let's get creative and see who comes out on top!

fields.name: Animecon
fields.description: An evening filled with everything anime! We'll have many mini-events like karaoke, yakata try-outs, origami making, live pop quiz,  guess the opening, talks by prominent people from the anime industry, and a cosplay event.

fields.name: Art of Photoshop
fields.description: This is a photo manipulation contest where the teams will be given some number of pictures and they have to make an image using those number of photos using photoshop tools.

fields.name: Brandathon
fields.description: In this event, participants will be given a theme based on which a companys logo, typography and color palette has to be designed. The company can be real or imaginary.

fields.name: Monochrome
fields.description: Ever thought of the freedom of using only one color or hue and its different shade to build your art? This event gives you an online platform to depict the ruins of Bihar or monumental places in Bihar using shades of a single color.

fields.name: Lit Fiesta
fields.description: Take the quill and step into the literary era and take us into your own imaginative world. Put down your thoughts over the paper boats and share your embarrassing stories and funniest thoughts, share poems and shayaris you wrote in your little diary you never show!

fields.name: Proto UI
fields.description: This event is a UI/UX hackathon. A theme-based event where participants will be provided a problem statement on the basis of which they will have to design the wireframes and prototype of the product.

fields.name: Not So LAME Quiz
fields.description: Music, Entertainment, Literature, Art (MELA) Quiz

fields.name: Theatrix Workshop
fields.description: Workshop on introduction to Psycho-physical Theatre by Tarun Kohli (Movement Specialist & Yoga Instructor

fields.name: Fest Entry *Day 3
fields.description: Fest entry for Bollywood night

fields.name: Dance Workshop
fields.description: Hip Hop dance workshop by Akshit Juyal from HipHop International

fields.name: A Moveable Feast
fields.description: Travel, Living and Culture Quiz

fields.name: Trivial Trifecta
fields.description: Mini-quizzing fest featuring 3 quizzes - "The General quiz", "Not so LAME quiz", "A Moveable Feast". Register for all three at discounted price.

fields.name: Fest Entry *All Three Days
fields.description: Fest Entry for All Three Days

fields.name: Mr & Ms Anwesha
fields.description: A title event of Anwesha consisting of group discussion, personal interviews, and a fashion show. A fashion show to show your ramp walk and moves and to flaunt your fashion sense.

fields.name: Graffitti Workshop
fields.description: Workshop on Graffiti art by Sanatan Vatsyan aka JAXXER
